1.Add Snyk token to Jenkins Credentials
Go to Jenkins → Manage Jenkins → Credentials → Global → Add Credentials.

Select:
Kind: Secret text
Secret: <your Snyk token>
ID: Snyk-Token (this is what you reference in the pipeline)

